,Recommended,425720,28576969,"Posted: 23 December, 2016",all,Papa_Tyrant,"Okay so I put off writing a review for this because I wanted to make sure I knew how to use it properly.  Best mini golf game ever.  I've played a bunch and my wife has too.  We love being able to play turn based VR mini golf.  Add to it that there is a course editor and WOW,  just WOW.  For awhile I didn't know there was an advanced controls that allows you to orient your living room in relation to the golf course.  This was very beneficial for me as I use the Rift with two sensors right now.  I don't have complete room scale yet.  This keeps my forward vector in the nice area between my two sensors.  So I don't have to step over a wire and hope the touch controllers stay in view.  Thanks a bunch to the devs,  been looking for a VR title like this."
